Package uk.ac.ebi.brain.error

Exception Summary
BadNameException Exception thrown in case of problematic name for OWL entities.
BadPrefixException Exception thrown in case of problematic prefix
BrainException Generic type of expression
ClassExpressionException Exception thrown in case a class expression couldn't be parsed.
DataPropertyExpressionException Exception thrown in case a data property couldn't be parsed.
DataRangeException Exception thrown in case of problematic data range.
ExistingAnnotationPropertyException Exception thrown in case of an annotation property is already present.
ExistingClassException Exception thrown in case of a class is already present.
ExistingDataPropertyException Exception thrown in case of a data property is already present.
ExistingEntityException Exception thrown in case of an entity is already present.
ExistingNamedIndividualException Exception thrown in case of a named individual is already present.
ExistingObjectPropertyException Exception thrown in case of an object property is already present.
NamedIndividualException Exception thrown in case a named individual couldn't be parsed.
NewOntologyException Exception thrown in case of problem while creating a new ontology.
NonExistingAnnotationPropertyException Exception thrown in case of non existing query for an annotation property.
NonExistingClassException Exception thrown in case of non existing query for a class expression.
NonExistingDataPropertyException Exception thrown in case of non existing query for a data property.
NonExistingEntityException Exception thrown in case of non existing query for an entity.
NonExistingNamedIndividualException Exception thrown in case of non existing query for a named individual.
NonExistingObjectPropertyException Exception thrown in case of non existing query for an object property.
ObjectPropertyExpressionException Exception thrown in case an object property couldn't be parsed.
StorageException Exception thrown in case of storage problem.
